Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:22.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today's stage is set at a house of candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.01,0:00:24.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trick, a sugary-sweet, simple trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.76,0:00:26.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can be solved if you simply think outside the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:28.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing through the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.49,0:00:30.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looks like a child but has brain of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:07.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So then, the entrance fee for the museum is 500 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:10.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ecriture's cake is, on sale there for half-price!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:14.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we miss this chance, we'll regret it forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:18.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, the desserts won't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:20.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:23.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's here! It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:26.31,Signs,,0,0,0,,Ecriture
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:25.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:27.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright. we're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.94,0:02:28.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:30.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:33.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran! And the glasses kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:35.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.53,0:02:42.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is just like the one in the fairy tale "Hansel and Gretel."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:46.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were these all made from desserts?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.38,0:02:51.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are so many!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:52.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:55.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's start with conquering the first half for the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:57.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said, "start with."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:03:00.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does she mean, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:03.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Separated by lunch time, they'll have\Nmore treats in the afternoon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:05.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She says that we should just roughly\Nfill our stomachs in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:07.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that we can go at full strength in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:11.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to go back even more now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:15.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Candy House the Witch Lives In.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:23.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The pastry chefs all have their own display stands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:26.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should I eat first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person in this photo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Must be that man over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:15.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Making three different cakes at the same time is unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:23.27,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Maeda Tsuyoshi (26)\NPastry Chef
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:25.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looks like a Warrior Pastry chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:27.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:30.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He actually does have the "Warrior Pastry Chef" nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:33.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's that "Iron Pastry" chef?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.78,0:04:34.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:38.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one in the middle with the elegant movements\Nis called "The Prince of Pastries."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:39.91,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Fujino Yasou (30)\NPastry Chef
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:44.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, the inner most pastry chef said to\Nuse magic that makes sweets come to life,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:46.42,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Morimoto Yumi (26)\NPastry Chef
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:45.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's known as the "Candy Magician."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:05.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like a TV idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:09.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you want to try making it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.28,0:05:12.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.94,0:05:13.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:14.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:14.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:14.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:15.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:16.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:16.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about it, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:18.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you want to try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:21.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks pretty fun, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:22.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:24.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:28.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. It's very easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:29.06,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Sorry, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:29.70,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.13,0:05:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:30.85,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes! Yes!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:33.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:36.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not every day we come here, so why don't you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:40.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just follow a few very simple steps and you can do it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.93,0:05:42.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you finish it, I'll give it to you as a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:51.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Put a layer of chocolate cream on the cake\Nroll first. Make sure to get it a bit thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.98,0:05:56.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then use this fork to carve through the log pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:57.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:05:58.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fork?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:10.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the future, boys who know how to\Nmake pastries will be very popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.09,0:06:19.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think that's pretty good. Right, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.39,0:06:21.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.22,0:06:23.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's holding a grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me fix that for you, and I'll give it to you when I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:29.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll stay until the afternoon half, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:32.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:34.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:39.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! These candies look alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as expected from the "Candy Magician."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:54.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like it's made from glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.55,0:06:55.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:58.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This kind of invisible feel is the real magic behind the taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:06:59.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:03.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretty candy tastes better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:07.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've always dreamed of the day when I can use these desserts,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:10.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To take home first prize in a competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.86,0:07:16.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, this is so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.61,0:07:18.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:22.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which should I pick? It's so hard to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:23.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:25.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just pick one from every kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:26.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:34.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, don't drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:37.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll have this first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.01,0:07:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is good too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:42.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:43.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:43.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:44.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:45.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:46.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:49.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, glasses kid! Do you want me to get you something too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.39,0:07:51.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No need. I'm okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:54.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can get it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:55.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.36,0:07:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll take this, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:01.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dangerous, dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:08.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.98,0:08:12.80,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hashikaki Sachiko (45)\NEcriture Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:12.20,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:19.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry. Your cake is ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:21.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, don't worry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.30,0:08:23.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:25.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cake nowadays is also for your eyes to enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:28.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whether it's the ingredients or the cake itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:34.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can eat everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:36.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hard to believe, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:49.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maeda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, can't you be more enthusiastic\Nand go out to greet the customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:52.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you learn something from Fujino{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If greeting people can make things taste better,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:56.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll do that as much as you want me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:03.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're still able to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:04.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:07.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, have you been making your choice all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:08.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.93,0:09:11.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going all out in the afternoon half as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:16.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I'm kind of thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.73,0:09:18.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:20.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:22.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, please bring me something as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:28.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't eat any more sweet stuff for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or else Shinichi will probably say,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:34.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I haven't seen you for a while. Did you gain\Nsome weight?" or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:36.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:38.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:43.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a pastry chef, not a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:46.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's good enough, as long as the customers are happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:48.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please judge if based on the flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:52.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're too naive. Delicious desserts can be found anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:55.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the cake and chocolate dominated world of dessert-making,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:58.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Candy can only be sold this well due to my good management.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:00.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:14.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I came here yesterday, there wasn't a "make a wood\Nchocolate cake roll with the customer's help" event.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.79,0:10:15.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:18.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Sonoko, you were here yesterday too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:21.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No wonder she knows everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So here you guys are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:24.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:27.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the wood chocolate cake roll you made earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:28.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:33.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sure fixed it up well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:39.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you take off the surface, it's just like the ones sold outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:40.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks very delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is too cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:20.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The morning event ended around 12 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:22.60,Signs,,0,0,0,,Ecriture
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:23.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The body was found around 12:30 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During that time frame, where were you three?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:28.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I let the cashier out for lunch first,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:31.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And spent the rest of the time in the kitchen\Npreparing desserts for the afternoon event.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:35.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to look for them after I finished their cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:41.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about the owner, Hashikaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?\NWhere was she when you left?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was recording receipt data.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because she was really concentrating in doing\Nthat, I didn't speak to her when I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:51.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So after Fujino{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} left the building and before\Nhe handed the cake to Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:55.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit committed the crime within this short period.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you also outside, Maeda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:01.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was told that there was a call for ma in the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So from 12:25 pm. until about ten\Nminutes after, I was in the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You seem to remember the time very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:12.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's because I have a habit of looking\Nat clocks whenever I'm working.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:15.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I need to use the oven often.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:17.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was there anyone else in the office?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:18.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rest of the staff was out for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:22.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:24.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After Fujino{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} left this place,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone murdered Hashikaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:29.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the body was found by Maeda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nwho'd returned from the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:30.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:31.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were the only one who was here at the time, Morimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:38.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you notice anybody entering or leaving this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:39.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:42.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim died due to a heavy blow to the back of her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:45.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murder weapon might still be in this store.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:47.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Make sure to perform a detailed search for the murder weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:48.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:52.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the culprit is one of these three people,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:54.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is the murder weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:56.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And how they got rid of it is the key to this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:13:01.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maeda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Fujino{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}... One of\Nyou killed the owner, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:02.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:06.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:09.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maeda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} borrowed a large amount of money from the owner,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:11.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Fujino{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you'd been fighting with the owner\Nbecause you wanted to start your own store.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:14.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone in the store knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That may be true, but I'm not the only one\Nwho has a problem with the owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:19.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:25.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's very confident in her skill, so she didn't\Nwant to join the cake making event.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:30.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you have a fight with the owner\Nonly minutes before she was killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:31.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could even hear the noise from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:36.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that there was an argument between\Nthe owner and pastry chef, Morimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:39.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please judge it based on the flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:43.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Morimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} who had stayed behind alone\Ndid have a chance to commit the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.93,0:13:49.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a separator in all three kitchens\Nso you can't sea her from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:52.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there's a tree blocking the view here, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:55.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't see much from Morimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:58.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:04.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fujino{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} who went outside, and Maeda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nalso had a chance to commit the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:07.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You went out immediately after I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.12,0:14:10.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Giving the cake to the kid shouldn't have taken that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:14.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a big layout here. It took me a while to find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.46,0:14:18.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The timing of your phone call is really perfect too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:21.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the time I picked it up, the other person had already hung up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This proves that it was somebody's trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.22,0:14:26.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's also possible that you called the office yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:29.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And asked yourself to come to there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:29.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:31.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As soon as we find the murder weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:33.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll know who the culprit is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.27,0:14:38.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Out of the three of us, you're the most likely\None to have the chance to kill the owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:39.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were so many cakes here before. Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:52.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A woodchip?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:56.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, we couldn't find the murder weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:58.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. It didn't turn up, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:02.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you guys ever think of the possibility that\Nthe murder weapon has already been eaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it would disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:07.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, this is a candy house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:09.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using a dessert as a murder weapon isn't that farfetched.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:13.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A dessert made into a murder weapon... Who would eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we should still locate the type of desserts\Nthat could be used as weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cookies are impossible, it would break on contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:24.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't even need to mention pies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:27.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My chocolate is impossible too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:29.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because it's too soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:30.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:32.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that I used my candy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.37,0:15:34.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then ate the candy with her blood on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:37.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Candy might be big enough to be a murder weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:39.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's hard to eat by oneself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.17,0:15:41.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:42.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it melted!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:49.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Throw it in a heating pot so that it melts?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:50.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never done anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.31,0:15:54.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person who can distract others from the noise,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:56.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And who was alone here... She's the only\None who could commit the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:15:59.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:04.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the detectives finish checking the pots\Nin your kitchen, everything will be clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:07.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is she the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've always dreamed of the day when I can use these desserts,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:11.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To take home first prize in a competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:26.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:28.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected, it's hand to believe that it was her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.27,0:16:36.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:45.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are there woodchips in the kitchen too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.53,0:16:50.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I came here yesterday, there wasn't a "make a wood\Nchocolate cake roll with the customer's help" event.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:51.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:16:59.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been used by you. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.42,0:17:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I won't let you stay freely outside the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:06.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, the culprit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:10.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:12.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:13.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.31,0:17:20.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, it wasn't Morimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, did that feeling come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:23.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:27.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To let the owner recognize the flavor of her desserts,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:30.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's been working very hard to prepare\Ncandy for the afternoon half.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.99,0:17:33.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As evidence, in her kitchen,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:35.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are candies that she wanted the owner to taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:40.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take what's in my left hand and show it to everyone, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.51,0:17:52.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:55.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This doesn't look like something half-way done or a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.23,0:17:57.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That little candy is the best proof that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.35,0:18:01.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wanted to use the flavor of her candy to reach the owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.48,0:18:03.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to let the owner try it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:06.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, just who is the murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:07.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The real murder is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Prince of Pastries, Fujino{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:13.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, you used the phone to get Maeda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.75,0:18:22.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And used your chance when Morimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nwas using the mixer in her kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:27.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can say for sure that there's no way to\Nsee Morimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s kitchen from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:30.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fujino{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} used this blind spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.18,0:18:32.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:33.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:44.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.82,0:18:53.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying I hit her with my candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.83,0:18:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:55.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murder weapon is the wood chocolate cake roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.62,0:19:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A wood chocolate cake roll? How can such\Na soft thing be used as a murder weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.54,0:19:03.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright. Let me explain, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:06.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This house is called "The Candy House."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:08.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And with a rough look around, it looks\Nas if you could eat everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.51,0:19:11.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But in reality, it's just a wooden house\Noutfitted with a candy surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.72,0:19:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fujino{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} got his inspiration from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:17.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And used the cake to cover the real weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're saying that he made the murder weapon\Nlooks like a wood chocolate cake roll?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.15,0:19:25.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Correct. The murder weapon is actually a log.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:28.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you'd thought ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:32.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You first hid a wooden log that was slightly smaller\Nthan the wood chocolate cake rolls in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.45,0:19:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you hid the log under the tray\Nthat carried Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:45.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then you took the log out and swung it at Hashikaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:49.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's your evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:52.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The evidence is there in the middle,\Non your display stand, Fujino{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:55.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, go take the wood chocolate cake roll here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.18,0:19:56.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:04.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.36,0:20:06.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Onee{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.82,0:20:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, It's on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:15.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So give everyone half of the wood chocolate cake roll each.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.24,0:20:16.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.34,0:20:30.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, there one that's too hard. I can't cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:32.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.22,0:20:34.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like there's a real piece of wood inside this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:40.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fujino{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} hid the real murder weapon\Ninside the chocolate cream,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:45.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And put the cake on the tray. and as he promised Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.19,0:20:49.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Walked out the door, with the real wood chocolate cake roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.16,0:20:57.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The owner was just like a real witch in this candy house.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:00.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She promised ma that if I won the pastry competition\Nand worked here for three years,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could start my own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.88,0:21:07.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But even though I won the competition with the wood\Nchocolate cake roll and worked for three years,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:11.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though I'd never complained and\Naccepted her abuse for three years,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:16.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That woman saw that I was popular and kept putting\Noff my wish to start my own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.43,0:21:18.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She told me she could make ma stop\Nmaking my wood chocolate cake roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.72,0:21:22.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She even said that we'd never agreed\Non something like my business plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:25.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:29.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll continue this at the police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.70,0:21:32.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shattering his dream of starting a business,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:36.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And taking away the wood chocolate cake roll\Nwhich has been with him from the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:40.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The owner was exactly like the witch in "Hansel and Gretel,"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.25,0:21:45.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who lured children into the forest to eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.18,0:22:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the wind I sometimes smile, sometimes cry, and sometimes fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.98,0:22:13.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two of us are just like this standing in front of our dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.24,0:22:18.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our dream is sure to be somewhere in the unknown future.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.45,0:22:35.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The colors of the seasons, always repeating let us experience a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.68,0:22:49.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I look upon the side of your sleepy face with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.44,0:23:03.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Staying in that moment, this becomes our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.39,0:23:19.30,Signs,,0,0,0,,Ecriture
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.97,0:23:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.48,0:23:23.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,AH!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.56,0:23:26.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My chocolate cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.44,0:23:29.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's ruined! What a shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.69,0:23:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.07,0:23:33.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If will be the same in your stomach anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.57,0:23:34.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.70,0:23:36.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.08,0:23:37.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.95,0:23:40.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can go to another shop that has good\Nchocolate cake next time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.33,0:23:43.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.42,0:23:45.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember, close to this station,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.50,0:23:47.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a delicious cake-baking shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.92,0:23:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.72,0:23:53.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a second. Right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.34,0:23:57.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey... For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.06,0:24:07.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If my deduction is right,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.73,0:24:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something is about to happen right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.32,0:24:13.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't let anything happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.82,0:24:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.75,0:24:28.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan: A Lucky Man's Suspense!
