Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.69,0:24:47.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.27,0:24:49.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.28,0:24:51.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next time also has strange title.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.02,0:24:54.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lucky people should be Inspector Megure and uncle...
